g.title: j1256197998
g.text: How do you do it, babas

g.title: j809029112
g.text: You forgot to tell me what you're talking about.

g.title: j2427518488
g.text: Being trapped for centuries without time
We are fantasmas haunting this place

g.title: j808078273
g.text: Lo siento, too much time in my head alone
Though less so recently between you and the bruja

g.title: j3033253568
g.text: You say you've done it in Duviri
That Kingdom of Death and Stories
I'm worried I will lose my mind, now

g.title: j3723376877
g.text: You say you've done it before
In this other land of yours
I'm worried I will lose my mind, now

g.title: j1327475063
g.text: Honestly? I almost did. I chose to go numb instead.

g.title: j325719057
g.text: I... think I did lose my mind for a little while. I don't remember whole chunks of it.

g.title: j3075783364
g.text: What happened to me in Duviri is very different to what's happening here. You're not alone like i was.

g.title: j1592255025
g.text: But you came back to life it seems, I don't see that in you now

g.title: j2975577880
g.text: I've seen that in soldiers after bad battles, blocking it all out
The mind protects itself from the worst sometimes
It's for the best, babas, trust me

g.title: j927802807
g.text: Not the people I'd want to spend eternity with, babas

g.title: j99447070
g.text: Once I realized what was happening, I fought like hell to keep from letting it consume me.

g.title: j604740920
g.text: I had help from friends to pull me out of it.

g.title: j4057316354
g.text: I was only around to stitch them back together, before we were turned into monsters
Now we don't have a choice
You think they want me here?

g.title: j3891109890
g.text: I don't see a way out for us... do you?

g.title: j1603097248
g.text: You think the other Hex don't like you?

g.title: j3359584940
g.text: Well, maybe if you weren't so bitchy...

g.title: j3290555983
g.text: I mean, I can take you out of here via transference for short periods.

g.title: j1770373482
g.text: Just how much do you like me, babas
I've been wondering how quickly you'd break

g.title: j2496092866
g.text: You think I don't know that, babas?

g.title: j413241435
g.text: ¿Want to take me out for a walk?
Cuidadito, I am not going to be the pet of this relationship...

g.title: j371389355
g.text: I just want to be your friend, Lettie. No offense.

g.title: j1869512109
g.text: Why don't you let people get close?

g.title: j3586805245
g.text: You don't want to get hurt if you lose them.

g.title: j698342152
g.text: If I weren't I wouldn't be Lettie anymore
I am who I am babas

g.title: j3138168574
g.text: I guess we take bets on who goes crazy first

g.title: j2581949572
g.text: I was just trying to be nice. You're not my type.

g.title: j789771924
g.text: Do you want me to be?

g.title: j3156153360
g.text: It's safer this way for everybody

g.title: j1738108962
g.text: Do you know how long rats live?
I am used to losing my little panquecitos

g.title: j3516590866
g.text: Do you want me to be?

g.title: j527490534
g.text: Yeah, you're my type. I like to live dangerously. ;)

g.title: j799239789
g.text: No, I'd rather just stay friends.

g.title: j178785830
g.text: Just as a warning, I'm really stubborn, and I want to get to know you better.

g.title: j1509959003
g.text: Thanks for the heads up. I won't take it personally if you step all over my feelings.

g.title: j2228801460
g.text: And I love them more than humans
I am comfortable with grief and loss, more than you know
Do not pretend you know me babas

g.title: j3113793338
g.text: Yeah, you're my type. I like to live dangerously. ;)

g.title: j2362608128
g.text: No, I'd rather just stay friends.

g.title: j1520227744
g.text: Sí, friends is fine by me
That's more than enough for most people

g.title: j560836000
g.text: Someone like you would need to be to survive
I like the stubborn ones, though

g.title: j3719260979
g.text: It's not your feelings I want to step on
